quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,80,Kananjalo nabemi basemaweni babaphika abaProfeti
  15,81,Ke kaloku Sabanika Thina imiqondiso yeThu kodwa abakholwa kuyo
  15,82,Bona babesakha imizi yabo ezintabeni
  15,83,Kodwa sona isohlwayo sabafumana ekuseni ngesifingo
  15,84,Ke kaloku konke ababekusebenzele akuzanga kubancede nganto
  15,85,"Thina ke ASizanga Sidale amazulu nomhlaba nako konke okuphakathi apho ngaphandle kokuwadalela inyaniso. Kananjalo iYure yona iyeza ngokwenene, ke (wena Muhammad) yiba ngathi awuziboni iziphoso zabo ubuye ngenceba nemfesane (kubo)"
  15,86,"Inene iNkosi yakho nguMdali, uSolwazi"
  15,87,Inene Thina Sikuphe iSab’an minal mathâni8 ne’Kur’ân yonke
  15,88,"Ke kaloku wena maze amehlo akho angajameli izinto eSiziphe abathile kubo (abangakholwayo), ungabi buhlungu nokuba buhlungu ngazo. Yiba nenceba kwabakholwayo (amaMuslim)"
  15,89,"Yithi\tkubo\t(Muhammad):\t“Mna\tndinguMlumkisi ngokusekuhleni"
  15,90,Njengoko Sithumele kubahlula-hluli
  15,91,"Abenza\ti’Kur’ân\tibe\tzizahlulo\tngezahlulo\t(bakholwe kwinxalenye yayo bangakholwa kwenye)"
  15,92,"Inene (Ndifunga) ngeNkosi yakho (Muhammad), Siza kubabiza bonke beze embuzweni (ngezenzo zabo)"
  15,93,Ngako konke oko bakwenzayo
  15,94,"Wena ke vakalisa ngaphandle [ungawufihli (uMyalezo ka- Allâh)] lowo uyalelwe ngawo. Uzikhwebule kubakhonzi bezithixo"
  15,95,Inene Thina Siya kukwenza wanele uwedwa ngokuchasene nabagculeli
  15,96,"Abayamanisa omnye uthixo kuAllâh, kodwa baza kwazi kungekudala"
  15,97,"Inene, Thina Siyazi okokuba intliziyo yakho icinezelekile ngenxa yoko bakuthethayo"
  15,98,"Ke wena zukisa ngendumiso iNkosi yakho, ube ngomnye wabo baqubudayo kuYo"
  15,99,Uyinqule iNkosi yakho kananjalo kude kufike isiqinisekiso esiyinyani (ukufa)